window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The final showdown.</p> <p>Jasmine is on a mission. The threat from her father is growing stronger, and she must pull together a group powerful enough to end the threat he poses.</p> <p>The enemy of her enemy is her friend. The problem lies in the rivalries between the various groups in Jasmine's world.</p> <p>To get around the issue, Jasmine hides her meetings from the pack as she creates allegiances with both friends and enemies of her people.</p> <p>Tension grows within the pack, and their trust in Jasmine is shaken. All the while, a dark cloud looms in the distance.</p> <p>In this final showdown, Jasmine must overcome her tendency to operate alone and show her true skills as a leader.</p> <p>Can she overcome the odds stacked against her and eradicate the end-of-world her father is threatening with his powers of necromancy?</p>"; 
